These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, british, thai
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, february, may
House: gothic-revival, victorian, farmhouse, colonial
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, snooker, domino
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the indonesian##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the victorian house##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is the egyptian##1
 6. the victorian house is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the farmhouse house is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the british is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is the egyptian##1
10. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality          | indonesian    | british      | egyptian  | thai     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Birthday   | october       | december | february     | may    |
| House   | colonial | victorian         | gothic-revival  | farmhouse    |
| Game           | snooker      | domino       | monopoly | chess |

