.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, plum, papaya, cherry
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike, car, quad-bike
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, magic-tricks, photography, singing
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rat
There are 4 different nationalities: british, chinese, nigerian, australian
 1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the british##1
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the chinese##1
 3. the australian is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 6. the nigerian is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person driving the car is the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far right##1
11. the person eating papaya is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Food      | plum      | tomato     | papaya    | cherry |
| Transport   | snowmobile | trike   | car   | quad-bike           |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | singing     | photography    | reading         |
| Pet           | rat         | hamster | pony     | ferret        |
| Nationality         | british     | australian  | chinese | nigerian       |

