.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, blues, classical, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, french
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, december, march
House: modern, farmhouse, colonial, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, coral, ivory, white
 1. the modern house is on the far left##1
 2. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the fan of classical is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 6. the person who likes white is the fan of classical##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 8. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 9. the french is the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the british is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
12. the fan of classical is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Music-Genre          | rock    | trance      | classical  | blues   |
| Nationality   | french     | chinese      | british | american      |
| Birthday           | january       | february         | march  | december         |
| House         | modern | farmhouse | colonial  | art-deco |
| Color     | ivory       | azure         | white   | coral        |

