The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, october, december
City: venice, liverpool, nizza, edinburgh
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
11. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Game      | whist   | billiard   | poker      | backgammon     |
| Sport          | soccer     | volleyball   | parkour | snowboarding |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
| Birthday           | march       | november      | december     | october |
| City     | venice    | nizza     | edinburgh     | liverpool     |

