There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, blue, blood-red, ivory
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, daisy, orchid
 1. the dancer is the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
 4. the person who growsrose is the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the musician is on the far right##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 8. the person who growsorchid is the dancer##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
11. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person playing poker##1
14. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre          | disaster       | romance     | crime     | thriller  |
