.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, azure, brown, yellow
City: hamburg, marseilles, paris, san-francisco
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, eggplant, pear, apple
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, milk, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, van
 1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person eating pear##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 9. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking milk is the person driving the van##1
11. the person who likes brown is the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the person eating pear is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Color         | azure   | brown | yellow    | grey  |
| City   | san-francisco    | hamburg | paris      | marseilles |
| Food   | pear | zucchini | apple         | eggplant  |
| Beverage         | 7up  | milk     | tea | sprite     |
| Transport     | bike      | van       | ship         | car         |

