4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, poker, bridge
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, davidoff, ritmeester, bluemaster
 1. the videographer is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the firefighter##1
 3. the police-officer is the person playing whist##1
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
