 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the videographer##1
 8. the police-officer is on the right of the person eating apple##1
 9. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the police-officer is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
11. the police-officer is the havana-smoker##1
12. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
