11. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the victorian house##1
12. the turkish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Nationality    | italian     | polish  | chinese       | turkish      |
| House       | modern    | palace        | gothic-revival  | victorian      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | time-travel          | mystery         | adventure      |
| Flower   | orchid     | begonia     | daisy       | amaryllis          |

