.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, security-guard, dancer, chef
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
City: berlin, venice, hamburg, london
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, indie, jazz, punk
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, monopoly, snooker
 1. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
 2. the security-guard is the person traveling to london##1
 3. the dancer is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the dancer##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the chef##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 9. the person playing whist is the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
11. the dressmaker is on the right of the security-guard##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
