.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, canasta, poker
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, sudoku, video-games
City: marseilles, san-francisco, london, paris
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, water, sprite
House: wooden, victorian, modern, tower
 1. the person traveling to paris is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the person drinking water is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the victorian house is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is the wooden house##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
10. the person playing poker is the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the modern house##1
12. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Game        | scrabble    | poker        | billiard        | canasta      |
| Hobby       | sudoku       | fishing       | skydiving      | video-games |
| City         | san-francisco | paris | london | marseilles      |
| Beverage         | cola          | sprite         | milk           | water    |
| House   | modern         | victorian       | tower     | wooden   |

 